rows.label: qst710803_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, this is rare. Someone other than
me coming to such a hidden spot.

rows.label: qst710803_msg0002
rows.name:
Are you here for fishing too? No,
it's my first time here as well...

rows.label: qst710803_msg0004
rows.name:
...My wife, Chiko, asked you to
look for me since I went missing?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0006
rows.name:
I just came here to fish for
a replacement for the fish
that disappeared from Iira.

rows.label: qst710803_msg0007
rows.name:
...What! The fish are already back?
Fisshi-san asked you to do it?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0008
rows.name:
I see, so that's what
happened. Then... hmm?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0009
rows.name:
Come to think of it, did you say
"my wife, Chiko, asked you"...?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0013
rows.name:
Th-that sounds scarier than
the Heaven's Holy Grail...

rows.label: qst710803_msg0014
rows.name:
An-anyway, I'm going back!
Thanks for letting me know!
